<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The send method for smtp reuses an established connection for sending mail, but it doesn't check if the connection timed out.</p>

<p>Of course this only occurs when running a php script longterm, as in a daemon context.</p>

